by keradus at 2018-01-06T15:06:52Z

you need to replace references to old fixer class to new fixer class:
```
ker@dus:~/github/PHP-CS-Fixer$ grep -r NoMultilineWhitespaceBeforeSemicolonsFixer src
src/Fixer/LanguageConstruct/CombineConsecutiveIssetsFixer.php:        // should ran before NoMultilineWhitespaceBeforeSemicolonsFixer, NoTrailingWhitespaceFixer, NoWhitespaceInBlankLineFixer and NoSpacesInsideParenthesisFixer.
src/Fixer/Import/SingleImportPerStatementFixer.php:        // must be run before NoLeadingImportSlashFixer, NoSinglelineWhitespaceBeforeSemicolonsFixer, SpaceAfterSemicolonFixer, NoMultilineWhitespaceBeforeSemicolonsFixer, NoLeadingImportSlashFixer.
src/Fixer/Semicolon/SpaceAfterSemicolonFixer.php:        return -1; // Must run after NoMultilineWhitespaceBeforeSemicolonsFixer
src/Fixer/Semicolon/NoEmptyStatementFixer.php:        // should be run before the BracesFixer, CombineConsecutiveUnsetsFixer, NoExtraBlankLinesFixer, NoMultilineWhitespaceBeforeSemicolonsFixer, NoSinglelineWhitespaceBeforeSemicolonsFixer,
```

after you replace the comments here, you need to replace the references in:
```
ker@dus:~/github/PHP-CS-Fixer$ grep -r no_multiline_whitespace_before_semicolon .
./tests/AutoReview/FixerFactoryTest.php:            [$fixers['combine_consecutive_issets'], $fixers['no_multiline_whitespace_before_semicolons']], // tested also in: combine_consecutive_issets,no_multiline_whitespace_before_semicolons.test
./tests/AutoReview/FixerFactoryTest.php:            [$fixers['no_empty_statement'], $fixers['no_multiline_whitespace_before_semicolons']],
./tests/AutoReview/FixerFactoryTest.php:            [$fixers['no_multiline_whitespace_before_semicolons'], $fixers['space_after_semicolon']], // tested also in: tests/Fixtures/Integration/priority/no_multiline_whitespace_before_semicolons,space_after_semicolon.test
./tests/AutoReview/FixerFactoryTest.php:            [$fixers['single_import_per_statement'], $fixers['no_multiline_whitespace_before_semicolons']], // single_import_per_statement,no_multiline_whitespace_before_semicolons.test
```

and finally the itest files (both, configuration in them and their file names)

